headline: Nordnet AB Selects Shareholder Disclosure Solution from Broadridge
summary: In line with its obligations under the updated Shareholder Rights Directive (SRDII), Nordnet Bank AB, a leading pan-Nordic digital platform for savings and investments, has commenced live operations with an international shareholder disclosure solution from global Fintech leader, Broadridge Financial Solutions, Inc. (NYSE:BR).
